Package: glottospace
Type: Package
Title: Language Mapping and Geospatial Analysis of Linguistic and Cultural Data
Version: 0.0.75
Author: Sietze Norder
Maintainer: Sietze Norder <mail@sietzenorder.nl>
Description: The R package glottospace helps users to do geospatial analyses on linguistic and cultural data. 
    Examples include: matching linguistic datasets to their location, 
    calculating distances between languages based on linguistic features, 
    visualizing linguistic data on a map.
URL: https://github.com/SietzeN/glottospace
BugReports: https://github.com/SietzeN/glottospace/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    Hmisc,
    magrittr,
    mapview,
    purrr,
    rnaturalearth,
    sf,
    tmap,
    rnaturalearthdata,
    curl
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
